The gMol program has the following external dependencies:
  Qt (http://qt.nokia.com/products/) and it's associated dependencies, specifically
    1. OpenGL
    2. SQLite3 
    3. WebKit
Portions of the gMol system's associated independent processes depend on:
  1. OpenBabel (http://www.openbabel.org) or use your package manager under linux
  2. SQLite3 (http://www.sqlite.org)

Parts of gMol (gramps) use the gfortran compiler, which you will probably have to
install.  Mingw includes gfortran (http://www.mingw.org/wiki/MinGW).
Use your package manager under linux.
For OSX, start here: (http://www.macresearch.org/xcode_gfortran_plugin_update)
